urls.title: Travelers have 6 months to upgrade to REAL ID for air travel
urls.description: Starting May 3, 2023, every air traveler 18 years of age and older will need a REAL ID-compliant driver’s license, state-issued enhanced driver’s license, or another acceptable form to fly within t…

data.text: Your ID must comply or you won’t fly! Starting 5/3/23, you’ll need a state-issued REAL ID compliant license or identification card—or another acceptable form of ID (such as a passport)—to fly within the U.S. Get ahead now by reading more: https://t.co/xzOj0QeJZM https://t.co/uDV1H6zuRa
